summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting a deed from the State of Washington to portions of Blocks 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, 13, 14 and 15, Hutchinson's Div. of Green Lake Add. to the City of Seattle, and Block 5, Fairview Add. to Green Lake, and Block 1, Sharpless Add. to the City of Seattle, together with the alley in said Block 1; Block 2 Epler's Div. of Green Lake Add., together with the alley in said Block 2; and portions of 4th Ave. NE, 5th Ave. NE, 6th Ave. NE, NE 75th St., NE 76th St., NE 77th St. and NE 78th St. abutting upon or adjacent to said Blocks in said Adds. (NE 75th St. to NE 80th St. Frontage Road); and repealing Ordinance No. 101769, which contained an error in the description in Section 2, Par. 5 thereof.
